main_text: This embedded programmable logic controller (PLC) includes customer-specific software with flexible count and type of IOs and/or standard interfaces.
benefits: Customer-specific software based on Renesas' Flexible Software Package (FSP)
Option to add industry-approved software stacks (e.g. EtherCAT)
Flexible selection of IOs and/or standard Analog + Digital IOs
Wired interface like RS-232, RS-485, IO-Link, ASi-5, Ethernet, USB
Wireless interface like BluetoothÂ®, LTE-M, NB-IoT

applications: Small embedded control for industrial use and/or home automation etc. using standard IOs or I/F
Optional central GUI via BT or IoT
Examples:Simple control for smart home refrigerator, oven... with an additional smartphone appPLC for industrial Ethernet with Sensors + Controls and smartphone for GUI/debug/commissioning
